  <h3>Clinical Skills</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Nursing Process: Assessment</li>
    <li>Nursing Process: Diagnosis</li>
    <li>Nursing Process: Planning</li>
    <li>Nursing Process: Implementation</li>
    <li>Nursing Process: Evaluation</li>
    <li>Documentation and Reporting: Change-of-Shift Hand-off Report</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="key-terms">Key Terms</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>ADPIE:</strong> Assessment, Diagnosis, Planning, Implementation, Evaluation.</li>
    <li><strong>CJMM:</strong> Clinical Judgment Measurement Model – six cognitive skills framework.</li>
    <li><strong>NANDA:</strong> North American Nursing Diagnosis Association – standardized nursing diagnoses.</li>
    <li><strong>SBAR:</strong> Situation, Background, Assessment, Recommendation – structured communication tool.</li>
    <li><strong>SMART goals:</strong> Specific, Measurable, Achievable, Realistic, Time-bound.</li>
    <li><strong>PES format:</strong> Problem + Etiology (related to) + Signs/Symptoms (as evidenced by).</li>
  </ul>
